Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ride on that wind, and get it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:35.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:38.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she? Where is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:47.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she? Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:50.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that woman go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:57.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a part-time job, then you should work at the beach! At a beach house!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the beach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll meet someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:02.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That could happen! It'll happ-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:05.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all muddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:21.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is there a shrine nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's a shrine once you pass through thoses bushes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:29.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:36.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That was some crazy wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a strange guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't talked much ever since he transfered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of hard to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,"What are you doing," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:01.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous that you can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:06.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:12.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was small, I would sometimes see strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They were probably the ones called Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They were never really friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but ever since I moved here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,there have been some who randomly pick fights, and it's been quite problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:25.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, and if I run away to a shrine-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally got you, Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, return it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:44.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, it'll be a bother if your name is called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:51.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull out her tongue so that she can't call your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Her tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, she got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We only need three plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:22.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We need one for our guest over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:30.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The child was saying some strange things again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He just wants attention. He's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing there, Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something {\i1}is{\i0} there! Look carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right there! It's looking right at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier that sealed me has been broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:22.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not working...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a precious human, to not bumble at the sight of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:14.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Impudent brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:22.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Natsume Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:27.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you, Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume Reiko was my grandmother's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:39.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandmother? What, you're her grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:42.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. If I look carefully, you're a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to look carefully to discern that I'm a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:49.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike humans, we do not particularly concern ourselves with gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew my grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she lived near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She was quite the beautiful human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like you, she was able to see Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the humans around her could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No one was able to understand Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:15.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always, always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:29.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko began to confront the Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:32.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of the Book of Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it was my grandmother's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome back, Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Your face is all pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your uniform is all muddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Fell? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you injured? Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:24.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:26.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens, just tell me. You don't need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Being naughty is fine, but keep it to a minimum, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:40.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:52.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell Touko-san that I was being chased by Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her to be creeped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:05.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Having lost my parents early, I moved from place to place among my relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:14.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have been living with people who are somehow connected to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I began to live in this house last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother also lived on this land once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:32.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She passed away, but like me, she had the power to see things that others couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:36.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of it, she was shunned by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:43.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's somewhere among the things I inherited...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:47.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what that fortune cat was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something you should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-kun! What was that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:22.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going shopping for a bit, so watch the house, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, give me the Book of Friends too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:38.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, no, no! Let me out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand me the Book of Friends after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll leave him alone for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave after you eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You freeload here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you're just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "cat?" How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This fortune cat form is not my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My true form is quite elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a cat, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is just used to this form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. Just eat that quickly and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:28.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:33.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you have the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I also owe you for breaking the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:41.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your bodyguard from now on, so call me "sensei."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:42.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:47.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you don't know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:56.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Within the Book of Friends are the names of the Ayakashi that Natsume Reiko defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:58.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Names?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:03.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko challenged the Ayakashi she met, one after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she was born with immense spiritual power, she was undefeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:11.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And those who lost
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,were made to write their names on paper as proof of their subordination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:19.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends is composed of those who wrote their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're the names of Youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:25.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that they cannot defy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:29.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who holds the contracts and calls their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, if you have the Book of Friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:37.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,you are able to control the Ayakashi linked with the names in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Dangerous, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:42.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stuck beside your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:51.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why you want this, Nyanko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you idiot! Don't treat it so carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:57.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that if you damage the characters, you'll hurt the one who has the name as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean you're in this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:04.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Like heck I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you how delicate it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'd lose to someone like Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you sealed away, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:21.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-Ah, well, there are some meaningful reasons for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No! More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:28.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,the Book of Friends' power is much more immense than you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:35.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the Ayakashi with their names in it are desperately searching for Natsume Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, the person living here is away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:57.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back, Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:03.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand me the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Return it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you planning to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:27.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide in that bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:43.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something a human can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:45.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand well now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:54.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You're just a human. Do you plan to supersede the Ayakashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:15:01.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what? What other purpose is there besides that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:03.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I planned to wait until you changed your mind, but forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's going to use it for bad things, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:24.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It's such an interesting object.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important inheritance from my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:48.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that she couldn't get along with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There are barely any people that remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She died young,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:16:00.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so as her only blood relative, I want to hold on to our link and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:03.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of it as another person's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to return them, so what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:11.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Return them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:15.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The names. I want to give them back to the Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool. Don't do it, it's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, there are some evil ones in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many lives you might have, it won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:27.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with me, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:31.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do what Reiko-san left undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:36.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die along the way, then you can have the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your power, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:47.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume, can I really have the Book of Friends when you're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:54.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, I will witness it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Reiko! I'll pull her tongue out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You want the Book of Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:15.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have the Book of Friends, I'll be the master of this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:18.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what you want too, Madara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:21.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me together with you, you vulgar bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:22.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you imagine their form,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,open the book, and then pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,One who would protect me, show your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:48.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost and never appear before me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:59.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What you need next is Reiko's saliva and breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,As her blood relative, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear out the contract and bite on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:07.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Put you hands together with force and concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, blow a whiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My steamed bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:42.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your spirit is filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:46.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want some good steamed buns, then I recommend the ones from Nanatsuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanatsuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:51.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, if you fight with me and you win,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:05.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's my win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that a surprise attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A win is a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:20.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now you're one of my followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that injury on your cheek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:32.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone threw a rock at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They said I was creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:38.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have a pretty name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my follower now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so when I call your name, you have to come flying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't call me today either?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:22.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lonely! A lot more than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Return it! Return my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:31.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long I wait, you never call my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:38.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hishigaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:47.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay by yourself now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:51.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure my grandmother wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hishigaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:21:00.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,my dear grandmother's kind-hearted friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:16.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:17.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a mean person, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can do it, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:37.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, I can't come to like the Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:45.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, they say the steamed buns there are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Let's go eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be so wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:51.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether good or bad, it was a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Can cats eat sweet things?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:03.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Some steamed buns, please!
